00:10:41,307 --> 00:10:43,017
on the "Fist of
the North Star" one.

278
00:10:43,017 --> 00:10:44,102
(laughing)

279
00:10:44,102 --> 00:10:45,436
Pachinko's for old men.

280
00:10:45,436 --> 00:10:46,771
