00:11:00,618 --> 00:11:02,453
It's the perfect plan.

289
00:11:02,453 --> 00:11:04,497
But the faculty room
is on the third floor.

290
00:11:04,497 --> 00:11:06,541
‐Is that okay?
‐Well, I haven't been practicing

291
00:11:06,541 --> 00:11:08,334
my wall riding for nothing.

292
00:11:08,334 --> 00:11:10,461
Ahh, good to know.

293
00:11:10,461 --> 00:11:11,546
(wind howling)

294
00:11:11,546 --> 00:11:13,756
T‐‐Tom‐Tom, what
are you doing here?

295
00:11:13,756 --> 00:11:15,300
G‐good evening, ma'am.

296
00:11:15,300 --> 00:11:16,509
Shut up!

297
00:11:16,509 --> 00:11:19,637
Orihara said he was going to
hide under his desk all night.

298
00:11:19,637 --> 00:11:22,849
