you'll fall right into his trap.

299
00:11:22,849 --> 00:11:24,517
I don't want to be held back.

300
00:11:24,517 --> 00:11:26,019
You guys really are stupid.

301
00:11:26,019 --> 00:11:28,521
At this rate, we'll still
be stuck in middle school

302
00:11:28,521 --> 00:11:29,981
